name: Metaverse Memories #2
description: A picture with @fdoganis (left) and @patricktresset (right) who was the first to try our H=N Metaverse prototype after seeing our progress. He asked "What do I look like? Is there a mirror?". Since there wasn't any I took this picture of the computer screen and sent it to him, in pure hicathon style. We hope that this Metaverse will allow the best random encounters and happy collisions on H=N.
